			"id": "0ikM0TFU",
			"x": 72,
			"y": 482,
			"width": 341.6015625,
			"height": 110,
			"text": "WISHLISTSERVICE  (wishlist.service.ts)\n\ngetWishlist(userId)\n  → delegates to repository, returns wishlist + games\naddGame(userId, gameId, gameName)\n  → delegates to wishlistRepository.addGame()\ndeleteGame(id)\n  → delegates to wishlistRepository.deleteGameById()",
			"originalText": "WISHLISTSERVICE  (wishlist.service.ts)\n\ngetWishlist(userId)\n  → delegates to repository, returns wishlist + games\naddGame(userId, gameId, gameName)\n  → delegates to wishlistRepository.addGame()\ndeleteGame(id)\n  → delegates to wishlistRepository.deleteGameById()",
			"fontSize": 11,
