			"x": 742,
			"y": 482,
			"width": 302.9296875,
			"height": 110,
			"text": "BETTER-AUTH  (lib/better-auth.ts)\n\nauth.handler() → handles all /api/auth/* routes\nemail + password provider\nBearer plugin (token-based auth)\ntrustedOrigins: localhost:3000, gateway-service\nPrisma adapter → User, Session, Account tables\nBETTER_AUTH_SECRET + BETTER_AUTH_URL from .env",
			"originalText": "BETTER-AUTH  (lib/better-auth.ts)\n\nauth.handler() → handles all /api/auth/* routes\nemail + password provider\nBearer plugin (token-based auth)\ntrustedOrigins: localhost:3000, gateway-service\nPrisma adapter → User, Session, Account tables\nBETTER_AUTH_SECRET + BETTER_AUTH_URL from .env",
