			"y": 792,
			"width": 199.21875,
			"height": 162.5,
			"text": "PRISMA CLIENT\n(lib/prisma.ts)\n\nSingleton PrismaClient\n  → global reuse in non-production\n  → new instance in production\n\n@prisma/adapter-pg  (PrismaPg)\nPostgres driver: pg\n\nDATABASE_URL from .env\nModels: User, Session, Account,\n  Verification, Wishlist, Game",
			"originalText": "PRISMA CLIENT\n(lib/prisma.ts)\n\nSingleton PrismaClient\n  → global reuse in non-production\n  → new instance in production\n\n@prisma/adapter-pg  (PrismaPg)\nPostgres driver: pg\n\nDATABASE_URL from .env\nModels: User, Session, Account,\n  Verification, Wishlist, Game",
